monitronics international inc
Private Company









Company Profile
Sector: Consumer Discretionary
Industry: Commercial Services
Sub-Industry: Security Services
Monitronics International, Inc. provides security alarm monitoring services. The Company offers home security monitoring and alarm, personal medical alert, fire alarm, and carbon monoxide detector systems. Monitronics International serves customers worldwide.




