Company Summary


Founded in 1994, Monitronics International is one of the nation's largest, fastest-growing alarm monitoring companies. Headquartered in Dallas, we provide monitored security system services to more than 1 million residential customers and commercial clients through its network of nationwide, independent Authorized Dealers.At the heart of our operations is the Monitronics Central Station, which has consistently met or exceeded all UL, National Fire Protection Association, Central Station Alarm Association standards. With millions invested in our monitoring technology, we can provide reliable, uninterrupted security monitoring service.









