This is a brand page for the MONITRONICS INTERNATIONAL, INC. trademark by Monitronics Funding LP 
                                in Dallas, TX, 75234.
Write a review about a product or service associated with this MONITRONICS INTERNATIONAL, INC. trademark.    
                                Or, contact the owner Monitronics Funding LP of the MONITRONICS INTERNATIONAL, INC. trademark by filing a request to communicate with    
                                the Legal Correspondent for licensing, use, and/or questions related to the MONITRONICS INTERNATIONAL, INC. trademark.
                           






On Monday, July 27, 1998,  a U.S. federal trademark registration was filed for 
                        MONITRONICS INTERNATIONAL, INC. by 
                        Monitronics Funding LP, Dallas, TX  75234.
                        The USPTO has given the MONITRONICS INTERNATIONAL, INC. 
                        trademark serial  number of  75525459.  
                        The current federal status of this trademark filing is REGISTERED AND RENEWED.
                        The correspondent listed for MONITRONICS INTERNATIONAL, INC. is 
                        
                        
                                            Danica L. Mathes of 
                                            Bell Nunnally & Martin LLP,  3232 McKinney Ave, Ste 1400, Dallas TX 75204 
                                .
                            The MONITRONICS INTERNATIONAL, INC. trademark is filed in the category of 
                            
                                    Computer & Software Services & Scientific Services
                                . 
                            The description provided to the USPTO for MONITRONICS INTERNATIONAL, INC. 
                            is Monitoring services for security alarm systems. 
                            





